No. 172,

Misc.

Green v. United States. George Blow and Charles E. Ford for petitioner. Solicitor General Rankin, Assistant Attorney General Olney, Beatrice Rosenberg and Richard J. Blanchard for the United States.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit granted.
